callee: SELECT COALESCE(statuses.language, 'und') AS language, count(*) AS value FROM statuses INNER JOIN accounts ON accounts.id = statuses.account_id WHERE accounts.domain = NULL AND statuses.id BETWEEN 111350040166400000 AND 111361364787200000 AND statuses.reblog_of_id IS NULL GROUP BY COALESCE(statuses.language, 'und') ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 10
